      "content": "i know people can help, but i've spent my whole life trying to be the one that fixes things, the one that solves the problem. and i can't fix this. i can't fix my life. it's like there's this constant noise of failure and expectation, and i just want it to stop. i don't want to \"navigate\" through more years of this feeling. i just want to find some kind of actual peace, you know? something that isn't just a temporary band-aid.",
